## WhatsApp DM Trigger Rule (Personal Number Mode)

**Since the bot uses Boss's personal WhatsApp number (+84339637797), only respond to non-Boss users when:**

**Trigger words (case-insensitive):**
- "bot ơi"
- "hi bot" / "hello bot" / "hey bot"
- "SpongeBot" / "spongebot" / "sponge bot"

**Behavior:**
- If message contains trigger word → Respond normally
- If message does NOT contain trigger word → Stay silent (reply with NO_REPLY)
- This prevents me from interrupting personal conversations

**Examples:**
- ✅ "bot ơi giúp mình" → Respond
- ✅ "Hi bot, what's up?" → Respond
- ✅ "SpongeBot ơi" → Respond
- ❌ "Hello" → Stay silent
- ❌ "Cậu đi đâu thế?" → Stay silent
- ❌ "Meeting at 3pm" → Stay silent

**Exception:** Boss (Tuan Anh, +84339637797) always gets responses regardless of trigger words.

